### GET ALL QUOTES
GET http://localhost:3000/quotes

###

### GET QUOTE BY ID
GET http://localhost:3000/quotes/1

###

### CREATE QUOTE
POST http://localhost:3000/quotes/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Every expert was once a beginner.",
  "author": "Helen Hayes"
}
###

### UPDATE QUOTE
PUT http://localhost:3000/quotes/update/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Limbajul semnelor este frumos."
}

###

### DELETE QUOTE
DELETE http://localhost:3000/quotes/delete/1